00:03:22.770 --> 00:03:23.880
So here's how you can do this.

00:03:23.880 --> 00:03:26.160
The first step is alignment.

00:03:26.160 --> 00:03:27.210
You really wanna make sure

00:03:27.210 --> 00:03:29.790
