00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:41.070
what do the viewers wanna watch?

00:04:41.070 --> 00:04:43.740
And then from that, you an
reverse engineer a video

00:04:43.740 --> 00:04:46.980
that would be interesting
to a majority of the niche.

00:04:46.980 --> 00:04:49.680
Now, a major power tip
here that is gonna help you

00:04:49.680 --> 00:04:53.010
