to use trend surfing.

00:04:53.010 --> 00:04:54.270
This is when you utilize,

00:04:54.270 --> 00:04:56.160
usually in your title and in your video,

00:04:56.160 --> 00:04:59.220
the most influential keywords, names,

00:04:59.220 --> 00:05:01.020
brands into your video.

00:05:01.020 --> 00:05:02.220
Now, once you have your idea,

00:05:02.220 --> 00:05:04.200
