00:05:04.200 --> 00:05:07.740
For the script, you really want
to be as concise as possible

00:05:07.740 --> 00:05:09.990
and leave no fluff in this script.

00:05:09.990 --> 00:05:12.150
Shorts are very quick
and you wanna make sure

00:05:12.150 --> 00:05:13.680
that you are getting to the point

00:05:13.680 --> 00:05:16.410
and getting to the next
point as soon as possible.

00:05:16.410 --> 00:05:18.120
Now, if you have a really long script

00:05:18.120 --> 00:05:20.640
or maybe you're wanting to take
one of your long-form videos

00:05:20.640 --> 00:05:23.100
and condense that into a Short,

00:05:23.100 --> 00:05:25.470
what you can do is go to ChatGPT

00:05:25.470 --> 00:05:27.900
and take that long-form
script and then ask it

00:05:27.900 --> 00:05:30.570
to summarize and shorten that script.

00:05:30.570 --> 00:05:32.580
Then you can use that for your Short.

00:05:32.580 --> 00:05:34.950
Step five is then to shoot your Short.

00:05:34.950 --> 00:05:36.060
And honestly, for Shorts,

00:05:36.060 --> 00:05:37.950
the gear really doesn't matter,

00:05:37.950 --> 00:05:40.470
but I like to think
